#: Game.Levels.PsetSets
msgid "# Problem Set: Sets\n"
"\n"
"You have completed four worlds of set theory:\n"
"- **Set World**: Sets as predicates, membership, ¬ß0/¬ß1\n"
"- **Subset World**: Subset relations, ¬ß2, ¬ß3\n"
"- **Set Operations World**: Union, intersection, complement, difference,\n"
