msgid "# Non-Membership with Existential Predicates\n"
"\n"
"In Level 3, you proved ¬ß0 ‚Äî the predicate was a simple\n"
"arithmetic comparison, and ¬ß1 dispatched it directly after ¬ß2.\n"
