#: Game.Levels.SetWorld.L09_Boss
msgid "Congratulations ‚Äî you have completed **SetWorld**!\n"
"\n"
"Here is what you now know:\n"
"\n"
"| Concept | Lean definition | Proof move |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| Set | ¬ß0 | ‚Äî |\n"
"| Membership ¬ß1 | ¬ß2 (predicate evaluation) | unfolds automatically |\n"
"| Set builder ¬ß3 | ¬ß4 | unfolds to ¬ß5 |\n"
"| ¬ß6 | ¬ß7 | ¬ß8 |\n"
"| ¬ß9 | ¬ß10 | impossible (¬ß11) |\n"
"| ¬ß12 | ¬ß13 | ¬ß14 with witness |\n"
"| Non-membership ¬ß15 | ¬ß16 | ¬ß17 then contradiction |\n"
"| Compound predicate | ¬ß18 | ¬ß19 then prove each part |\n"
"\n"
