msgid "# Monotonicity of Indexed Intersection\n"
"\n"
"In the previous level, you proved that indexed union is monotone:\n"
"if each ¬ß0, then ¬ß1. Now prove the\n"
"**dual** for indexed intersection:\n"
"\n"
"¬ß2\n"
